Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.68,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,1st Time on Gaki no Tsukai ya Arahende
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:06.62,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,"Which Looks Most Like Hamada!? Hamada Photo Contest!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.48,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,{\clip(28,966,590,1078)}When I entered the studio, without Hamada here it felt so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:16.66,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,When I entered the studio, without Hamada here it felt so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:21.03,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,From the moment you enter, you're surrounded by such a gentle atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.86,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,All of the staff are smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:25.90,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I thought it was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.60,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Thank you for mentioning the nice atmosphere during the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:32.37,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,This time, we went to a shopping district...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:36.31,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,...and anything that looked like Hamada-san, we took a photo of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.20,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Well everyone, this is Fuzashikōyama Shopping District.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.71,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Find Hamada-san and take a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.35,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Well then everyone, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.86,Matsumoto / Black,,0,0,0,,{\clip(360,998,568.5,1080)}Hamada has taken over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:51.46,Matsumoto / Black,,0,0,0,,Hamada has taken over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.06,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,More than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:04.33,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,It's a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:14.88,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's one here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.89,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,It's subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.49,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I thought I had it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:32.90,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Pretty much everything looks like Hamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:39.01,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,{\clip(178.5,942,514.5,1080)}Like I thought, looking underfoot is the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.81,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Like I thought,{\rYamasaki / Black} looking underfoot is the way to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.11,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,...for Hamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.53,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Ah, a bread shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:49.15,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,There'll definitely be something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.57,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,It's a little harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.28,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.40,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Surely one in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.40,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.35,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems so into this segment.
