Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.28,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,Maybe it looks too much like a {\rFujiwara / Black}monkey{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.45,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're that drone guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.44,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,Drone guy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.25,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,The drone comedian, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.25,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,I'm not a drone comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.82,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Give it your best, I'll be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.11,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,What's with the weird behaviour?
