Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.15,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,When he's in {\rEndo / Black}Guam{\r}, he probably looks something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.99,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,See the lips here.
