Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.22,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,We're back from the location shoot. What did you think Matsumoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:40.04,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,"There's so many Hamadas in this town."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:43.46,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,They were everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.66,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Of course Hamada-san isn't in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.06,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.26,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,But the company has no idea where he is.
