Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'd like to see a bunch of Hamada-san's emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take pictures of your various emotions.
