Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.15,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was his calf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.37,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Calf, do I have something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:19.35,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.71,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Could go either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.95,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,He did have something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.85,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,{\rMatsumoto / Black}I think this looks like {\r}Hamada close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.24,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's Hamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.24,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.48,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,A chestnut?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:39.55,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,A cross section of a chestnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:45.14,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad((320,320))\pos(720,880)\i1}At that time, Hamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.97,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's alright just doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:54.04,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,I see him quite a lot in his private time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:58.36,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,This is Hamada-san {\rInomoto / Black}playing golf early in the morning{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.82,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,He looks like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.82,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:07.70,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,It's a plug outlet covered up with putty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.20,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Hamada really appears everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.53,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Here's another Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.53,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.04,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,That's so Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.64,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Is that the backside of a shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.64,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,If you squish your shoes, it's Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.11,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,The face looks similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:28.12,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,It's scary close to Hamada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.35,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,He's in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:35.25,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,If it's a good mood, here's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.57,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This is a rare one, you might see it once a year or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.04,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,He's winking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.82,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,He had to have two good days in a row or else you wouldn't see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.40,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,{\rMatsumoto / Black}This is a truly happy{\r} Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:02.82,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,So happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.82,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,He's having a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:07.83,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This is a dead Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.53,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Just the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.88,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,He looks this featureless?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.88,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,This is... Yes, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:20.15,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,What sort of death causes that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.17,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,He passed away peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.04,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.35,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,I don't get any sense of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.35,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,Yes, very peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.96,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,The future Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.72,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,He's become a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.77,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,What the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.77,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.44,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,There's someone I'd like to introduce you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.67,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,He's a junior but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:20:00.18,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,...he seems to be imitating Hamada-san a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.18,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.68,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,Wes-P.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:11.65,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411,874)}Wes-P.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.52,Fujiwara / DrkGreen,,0,0,0,,The one who does the tablecloth skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.71,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Hamada just shows up everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:11.65,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,He's even appearing among the {\rMatsumoto / Black}juniors{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.62,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,He's infiltrated the juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:17.25,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Hamada seems to have aged a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:21.47,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This is the worn out Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.73,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Totally worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.71,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,He's looked like this since the start of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:34.61,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,This one definitely isn't Hamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:38.52,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,...but I found {\rTanaka / Black}Matsumoto-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.26,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Maybe a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.26,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,A few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.24,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Before the blonde hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.77,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,We've come to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.66,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,One more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.76,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Should we make this the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.50,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the most unbelievable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:07.21,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220.5,822)}*Not Abashiri Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:07.21,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san was at {\rInomoto / Black}Abashiri Prison Museum{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.02,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,The real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:11.61,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,It may have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.91,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.35,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Isn't this close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.04,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,He did look like that when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.16,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,Truly young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:37.08,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,The ones that are left aren't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.28,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.64,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.77,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Vegetables? Vegetable series.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.26,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I can't decide which one of these is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:01.31,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.63,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,There's just so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.93,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This one is him when he's super angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.74,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.77,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This one's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.93,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,There's also this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.78,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,...and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:20.95,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,Those three are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.46,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad((320,0))\pos(720,880)\i1}At that time, Hamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a caffè latte?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.29,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you adding sugar to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.86,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You add it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:36.82,Hamada / Black,,0,0,0,,It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:41.95,Hamada / Blue,,0,0,0,,Then why have you got ice cream in yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but does a caffè latte really need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.13,Hamada / Black,,0,0,0,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.89,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,We've come to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:07.53,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I would've gone with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:11.06,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5C5C62&\4c&H5C5C62&\fade(380,0)\pos(765,849.333)}Imabari City, Ehime Prefecture mascot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:11.06,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5C5C62&\4c&H5C5C62&\fade(380,0)\pos(774,933.333)}Barii-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.11,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,You've left the best 'til last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.53,Yamasaki / Green,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be lame to put this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:19.57,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,This ain't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:22.86,Tanaka / Purple,,0,0,0,,I had a lot that weren't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:26.21,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have another go at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.48,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,{\clip(240,914,854,1011)}If you looked all over Japan, you'd probably find some crazy stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.05,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,If you looked all over Japan, you'd probably find some crazy stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:35.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, have a look around your town and find the hiding Hamadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:40.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whatever it may be, people, things, animals, plants...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:42.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...If it looks like Hamada, anything is OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please visit the show's homepage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:49.71,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,That was a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:51.94,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,This one is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:53.93,Matsumoto / Red,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you use this in your home somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.95,Inomoto / Aqua,,0,0,0,,If your family was okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.00,Endo / Orange,,0,0,0,,It's like a funeral portrait.

